  "title": "Biome Grass Available",
  "description": "Makes the different colored grass blocks of different biomes available in the creative inventory! This mod is mainly for mapmaking purposes",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bLg0JOx.png\" width=\"517\" height=\"186\" /></p>\n<p><strong><br />Have any suggestion? Want to report a bug? We have a Discord server! You can join and ask anything you want!</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/U7ue38S2QX\"><img src=\"https://discord.com/api/guilds/922100907360018432/widget.png?style=banner2\" /></a><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><br /></span></p>\n<h2>Introduction</h2>\n<p>This mod aims to add the different kinds of biome colored grass blocks as creative-exclusive blocks! This mod is mainly directed towards mapmaking. If you are making a map and you need some specific color of grass without wanting to change the biome, you can use a block added by this mod! You can also place the different colored grass blocks next to eachother without them breaking the colors.<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><br /></strong></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>List of blocks added by this mod&nbsp;</h2>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p>* Badlands Grass<br />* Desert Grass<br />* Plains Grass<br />* Snowy Grass 1<br />* Snowy Grass 2<br />* Swamp Grass 1<br />* Swamp Grass 2</p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Screenshots</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/61nCnvg.png\" width=\"411\" height=\"109\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NdweUMK.png\" width=\"380\" height=\"196\" /></p>\n<h4><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></h4>\n<div id=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini\" class=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini_box\" style=\"background: initial !important; border: initial !important; border-radius: initial !important; border-spacing: initial !important; border-collapse: initial !important; direction: ltr !important; flex-direction: initial !important; font-weight: initial !important; height: initial !important; letter-spacing: initial !important; min-width: initial !important; max-width: initial !important; min-height: initial !important; max-height: initial !important; margin: auto !important; outline: initial !important; padding: initial !important; position: absolute; table-layout: initial !important; text-align: initial !important; text-shadow: initial !important; width: initial !important; word-break: initial !important; word-spacing: initial !important; overflow-wrap: initial !important; box-sizing: initial !important; display: initial !important; color: inherit !important; font-size: 13px !important; font-family: X-LocaleSpecific, sans-serif, Tahoma, Helvetica !important; line-height: 13px !important; vertical-align: top !important; white-space: inherit !important; left: 10px; top: 958px;\">\n<div id=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini_logo\" class=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini\" title=\"Traducir texto seleccionado\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div id=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini_sound\" class=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini\" title=\"Escuchar\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div id=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini_copy\" class=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini\" title=\"Copiar texto al Portapapeles\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini\" class=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini_box\" style=\"background: initial !important; border: initial !important; border-radius: initial !important; border-spacing: initial !important; border-collapse: initial !important; direction: ltr !important; flex-direction: initial !important; font-weight: initial !important; height: initial !important; letter-spacing: initial !important; min-width: initial !important; max-width: initial !important; min-height: initial !important; max-height: initial !important; margin: auto !important; outline: initial !important; padding: initial !important; position: absolute; table-layout: initial !important; text-align: initial !important; text-shadow: initial !important; width: initial !important; word-break: initial !important; word-spacing: initial !important; overflow-wrap: initial !important; box-sizing: initial !important; display: initia